These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, begonia, poppy, zinnia
1. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Flower   | aconite | begonia | poppy | zinnia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, november, january, april
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Birthday   | november | august | april | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, boat, subway, van
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the van is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | subway | boat | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-4::.
4 different games are played: canasta, poker, go, billiard
1. the person playing go is on the far right##1
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |  4  |
| Game   | poker | canasta | billiard | go |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, tea, coffee
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |  3   |     4      |
| Beverage   | coffee | tea | milk | hot-chocolate |

