3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3   |   4    |
| Transport   | snowmobile | roller | train | helicopter |

